{"tid":162302,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"[2017大師挑戰賽]古法魚蛋蒸腸","createTime":"2017-03-19T07:28:08.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-25T06:21:28.000Z","uid":4709,"like":84,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"626a5a782316012e442b5d3a13e6a172f7e1bf75","tid":162302,"uid":4709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T07:28:08.000Z","msg":"大家好，美國時間已經係夜深喇，我地呢d離鄉別井既打工仔好，學生哥好，望住個月亮就諗起家鄉既美食<br />\n所以今日我就教大家用美國買到既材料整魚蛋蒸腸！<br />\n<br />\n首先，大家既材料有：<br />\n魚蛋2粒（炸果隻亦得）<br />\n腸1條（你鍾意熱狗腸好，臘腸好都得，但本人嗜甜，所以簡香口既台腸）<br />\n蔥 適量<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/19/151110_d70e5c9a0b77084233e882698d5ace4a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F19%2F151110_d70e5c9a0b77084233e882698d5ace4a.jpg&h=7deee487&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n1：煲水<br />\n話明古法，當然要用沙煲（daiso買）<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2Cva8Pb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2Cva8Pb.jpg&h=ded48034&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2:準備材料<br />\n蔥可以用呢種五爪既刀開花，方便好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/19/151249_cdaf4f1d18751333cbe95117e5adca29.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F19%2F151249_cdaf4f1d18751333cbe95117e5adca29.jpg&h=066a3d1c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/19/151251_b73576222543b21877387ad432015576.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F19%2F151251_b73576222543b21877387ad432015576.jpg&h=1179d1ef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n雖然話古法，但現代中餐欠奉presentation<br />\n野食擺靚d,食果個都開心d<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n3:淋鼓油<br />\n記得用蒸魚鼓油，佢淡中帶甜，蒸野食一流<br />\n有要求既巴打記得用新開既鼓油，因為鼓油同空氣接觸之後會變味<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PQYh97f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPQYh97f.jpg&h=255e2b84&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/19/151641_73c40e9f3cbc00befa2b9468da5b5801.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F19%2F151641_73c40e9f3cbc00befa2b9468da5b5801.jpg&h=9d9c5418&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n4:蒸<br />\n係你準備好食材既同時，個水就差唔多滾，可以開始蒸<br />\n呢度我蒸左七分鐘岩岩好熟（視乎你用咩腸）<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9YQsGdU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9YQsGdU.jpg&h=7e1021f7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/19/151911_6a97969c774ce6c63a0a3d81af22ed7c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F19%2F151911_6a97969c774ce6c63a0a3d81af22ed7c.jpg&h=b33a27b7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n5:presentation!<br />\n同上，presentation係可以改變你食慾,所以擺碟擺靚d<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/883H37t.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F883H37t.jpg&h=7ef9c70c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/19/152034_af86f1c4a4cfb1f6f279144c891e6cb2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F19%2F152034_af86f1c4a4cfb1f6f279144c891e6cb2.jpg&h=e2b2f4fa&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/X6K7xZ0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FX6K7xZ0.jpg&h=21ff4319&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n6:食得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同上，因為本人嗜甜，所以食野鍾意落煉奶<br />\n但都係果句...presentation!<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7168b17.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7168b17.jpg&h=4ba70d03&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/19/152203_3485b507377ee9fb84a152ced09ffea7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F19%2F152203_3485b507377ee9fb84a152ced09ffea7.jpg&h=9cee996e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AA6595j.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAA6595j.jpg&h=fa510ed7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n評分：10/10<br />\n魚蛋+蒸魚鼓油好夾，岩岩好熟好彈牙爽脆<br />\n蔥又係岩岩熟，唔青得黎爽甜，唔會淋滋滋<br />\n腸更加係一絕，本身帶甜既台腸加上煉奶，佢地既甜味互相配搭，簡直係昇華左去另一個層次<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/19/152543_216a91993b992e11a4674f3ab8e45ca7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F19%2F152543_216a91993b992e11a4674f3ab8e45ca7.jpg&h=b8bcfe2c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/19/152545_0007017ad82df9d6729dff3fb4c09927.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F19%2F152545_0007017ad82df9d6729dff3fb4c09927.jpg&h=c47f25e8&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eD3SQ98.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeD3SQ98.jpg&h=20732247&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/27t5a3f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F27t5a3f.jpg&h=2460b806&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/19/152557_dec3b683cda9d4e01ce783c084c421a7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F19%2F152557_dec3b683cda9d4e01ce783c084c421a7.jpg&h=34a5867b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n好味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ff3a0973c9ae45205fed8031ae4df96b9f7a7eb","tid":162302,"uid":31296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T07:30:27.000Z","msg":"bam"},{"pid":"9c1fc02faf9d2975c5d9b52889